// ChatMessage Endpoints

### Get All Chat Messages
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages

### Get Global Chat Messages
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages/global

### Get Chat Message by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages/1

### Get Chat Message by ID (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages/99999

### Get Chat Message by ID (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages/invalid

### Get Player's Sent Messages
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/sent-messages

### Get Player's Sent Messages (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/sent-messages

### Get Player's Received Messages
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/received-messages

### Get Player's Received Messages (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/received-messages

### Get Player's Unread Messages
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/unread-messages

### Get Player's Unread Messages (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/unread-messages

### Get Conversation Between Two Players
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages/conversation/1/2

### Get Conversation (invalid IDs)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages/conversation/invalid/2

### Send Global Message
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "senderId": 1,
    "content": "Hello everyone! Good luck trading!"
}

### Send Private Message
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "senderId": 1,
    "receiverId": 2,
    "content": "Hey, want to trade stoves?"
}

### Send Message (missing content)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "senderId": 1
}

### Send Message (invalid sender)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "senderId": 99999,
    "content": "Test message"
}

### Mark Message as Read
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages/1/read

### Mark Message as Read (not found)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages/99999/read

### Delete Chat Message
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages/1

### Delete Chat Message (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/chat-messages/99999

### Get Player's Unread Count
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/1/unread-count

### Get Player's Unread Count (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/players/invalid/unread-count
